description:
Rachel Goodwin, NARS Director of Pro Artistry, talks Met Gala glamour, her ice cream obsession, and the most underutilized product in your kit. Before that, we chat about Jess's Bazaar new gig; Pat McGrath's divine new collaboration; the real deal on sugaring; and whether your skincare really works better at night.
